{"tid":1637980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 面 向 國 際 ]  勇武做完嘢，文宣又要發力喇","createTime":"2019-10-08T07:05:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T13:27:01.000Z","uid":218211,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"13e44c80cc5eaf6224493e39263970693f985b64","tid":1637980,"uid":218211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:05:36.000Z","msg":"代朋友Po<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前睇到有巴打Post話，宜家前線手足做野嘅速度快過文宣組好多，解釋唔到俾國際知我哋點解要咁做。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我就膽粗粗整咗幾個英文文宣，抛磚引玉，大家幫手，一齊整下、傳下！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n重點係：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">用Twitter！！！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">宜家好多外國tweet都係得幾百個retweet (周庭除外)，咁點推到俾國際睇呀！！！</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YU1o2ou.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYU1o2ou.jpg&h=8f8a9f76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dhuRrQa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdhuRrQa.jpg&h=83d08f6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u0YbrQb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu0YbrQb.jpg&h=903a6ced&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vwrTFad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvwrTFad.jpg&h=0c9fcb7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XwO60ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXwO60ae.jpg&h=bfa30b71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />